<p>The company may request an exit interview upon notice of termination. The purpose of the exit interview is to complete necessary forms, collect company property, and discuss employment experiences with the company.</p>', 61, TRUE, 2
FROM learn_modules m JOIN learn_categories c ON c.id = m.category_id
